#: bitcaster/dispatchers/handlers/gmail.py:35
msgid ""
"Simplified Email dispatcher for GMail accounts.\n"
"\n"
"**Generate Application password**\n"
"\n"
"- Navigate to your [Google Account](https://myaccount.google.com/security).\n"
"- Under the Password & sign-in method section, click App passwords.\n"
"- If requested login again using your usual password.\n"
"- Make sure Other (custom name) is selected in the Select app drop-down "
"menu.\n"
" Type the application name (ie. Bitcaster)\n"
"- Click Generate.\n"
msgstr ""
"Distributeur courriel simplifié pour comptes GMail.\n"
"\n"
"**Créer le mot de passe pour l'application**\n"
"\n"
"- Naviguer sur votre  [Compte Google](https://myaccount.google.com/"
"security).\n"
"- À la section Mot de passe & enregistrement , selectionner Mot de passe "
"application.\n"
"- Si nécessaire effectuer la login.\n"
"- S'assurer que (custom name) soit sélectionné \n"
"dans le menu déroulant.\n"
" Insérer le nom de l'application (par example Bitcaster)\n"
"- Cliquer Générer.\n"

#: bitcaster/dispatchers/handlers/hangout.py:72
msgid ""
"\n"
"#### Generate Application password\n"
"\n"
"- Navigate to your [Google Account](https://myaccount.google.com/security).\n"
"- Under the Password & sign-in method section, click App passwords.\n"
"- If requested login again using your usual password.\n"
"- Make sure Other (custom name) is selected in the Select app drop-down "
"menu.\n"
" Type the application name (ie. Bitcaster)\n"
"- Click Generate.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"#### Créer le mot de passe pour l'application\n"
"\n"
"- Naviguer sur votre [Compte Google](https://myaccount.google.com/"
"security).\n"
"- À la section Mot de passe & enregistrement , selectionner Mot de passe "
"application.\n"
"- Si nécessaire effectuer la login.\n"
"- S'assurer que (custom name) soit sélectionné \n"
"dans le menu déroulant.\n"
" Insérer le nom de l'application (par example Bitcaster)\n"
"- Cliquer Générer.\n"

